---
import LayoutPage from "@layouts/LayoutPage.astro";
---

<LayoutPage>
  <main class="p-4 py-12 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[48px_auto_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-8">
        <!-- Heading -->
        <h1
          class="h1 md:origin-top-right md:-rotate-90 md:-translate-x-12 md:translate-y-31.5 md:whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          <span>ABOUT</span>
        </h1>
        <!-- Horz Rule -->
        <div class="hidden md:block">
          <hr class="vr" />
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-10">
          <!-- About Text -->
          <section class="space-y-4 text-xl">
            <p>Hi, I'm Chris 👋</p>
            <p>
              Welcome to my humble showcase, featuring a few of my most
              prominent works. I'm a senior frontend developer and design
              engineer who has spent the last 20+ years building production web
              platforms and design systems, and crafting professional user
              experiences. I'm primarily self taught, and I still make time to
              research, tinker, and learn something new every day.
            </p>
            <p>
              I discovered my passion for programming and design while attending
              classes for Visual Basic and Photoshop in high school. I'm also a
              lifelong fan of video games, which all began when I received my
              first console as a kid, a classic Nintendo Entertainment System. I
              still remember the magic of picking up that controller and making
              Mario run and jump across the screen (occasionally to his untimely
              death). It was this that sparked my earliest interest in design
              and development.
            </p>
            <p>
              That passion grew into a career spanning a broad range of
              industries, including photography, corporate media, a digital
              agency, and a handful of tech startups. Along the way I created <a
                class="anchor"
                href="https://skeleton.dev/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer">Skeleton</a
              >, a free and open source UI library that has now achieved 150k+
              monthly downloads. I serve as its core maintainer and co-founded <a
                class="anchor"
                href="https://www.skeletonlabs.co/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer">Skeleton Labs</a
              > to support the project. It's been a privilege to work alongside some
              of the most talented and passionate people in the industry while building
              platforms for the web, video games, and open source.
            </p>
            <p>
              These days my focus is on agentic development and AI-augmented
              workflows. I put LLM technology to practical use, from importing
              and structuring site content to generating real design solutions
              for customers.
            </p>
            <p>
              I believe my strength lies not just in writing code or designing
              interfaces, but in solving real world problems. I pride myself on
              my ability to listen, learn, and help figure out what a project
              truly needs, then deliver at every step from concept to execution.
              Whether you're building a web application, looking to engage your
              audience, or carving a new path in the world, I'd love to help
              your project move forward on that journey.
            </p>
          </section>

          <hr class="hr" />

          <!-- Media Appearances -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <header class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 class="h3">
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-bold">{"["}</span>
                <span>Media Appearances</span>
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-bold">{"]"}</span>
              </h3>
            </header>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <iframe
                class="w-full aspect-video shadow-xl"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SLPBmP588Hk"
                title="Interview with Segun Adebayo, creator of Chakra UI"
                loading="lazy"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
              <iframe
                class="w-full aspect-video shadow-xl"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/txM-BCrZcbc?start=2561"
                title="This Week in Svelte"
                loading="lazy"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
              <iframe
                class="w-full aspect-video shadow-xl"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KxK9iA1ktlU"
                title="Speaker at the Svelte Summit"
                loading="lazy"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
              <iframe
                class="w-full aspect-video shadow-xl"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2OnJYCXJPK4"
                title="Speaker on the Svelte Sirens livestream"
                loading="lazy"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
          </section>

          <hr class="hr" />

          <!-- Resume -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <header class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <h3 class="h3">
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-bold">{"["}</span>
                <span>Resume</span>
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-bold">{"]"}</span>
              </h3>
              <a
                href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTXIHHD4NuQLXrSOJheUW6R-fJIKDrvt0R8VE5o9E1VmP7jTYybQziw01PC45jvAtM3-WP9CzqyRjXc/pub?embedded=true"
                class="btn preset-filled-secondary-500"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <span>View on</span>
                <svg
                  class="inline-block fill-current size-4 -translate-y-0.5"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 488 512"
                  ><path
                    d="M488 261.8C488 403.3 391.1 504 248 504 110.8 504 0 393.2 0 256S110.8 8 248 8c66.8 0 123 24.5 166.3 64.9l-67.5 64.9C258.5 52.6 94.3 116.6 94.3 256c0 86.5 69.1 156.6 153.7 156.6 98.2 0 135-70.4 140.8-106.9H248v-85.3h236.1c2.3 12.7 3.9 24.9 3.9 41.4z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                <span>&rarr;</span>
              </a>
            </header>
            <iframe
              class="bg-white shadow-xl"
              width="100%"
              height="800px"
              src="https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTXIHHD4NuQLXrSOJheUW6R-fJIKDrvt0R8VE5o9E1VmP7jTYybQziw01PC45jvAtM3-WP9CzqyRjXc/pub?embedded=true"
            ></iframe>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</LayoutPage>
